    <item>
      <title>Instacart 收入超出预期，聘请 Uber Vet 担任首席财务官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/instacart-names-new-cfo-as-revenue-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Instacart 将 Uber Technologies Inc. 前资深人士提升为首席财务官，接替即将退休的尼克·乔瓦尼 (Nick Giovanni)。这家杂货配送公司还报告了第一季度的收入超出了分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/instacart-names-new-cfo-as-revenue-beats-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 预计夏季旅游旺季前增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/airbnb-sees-growth-slowing-before-summer-travel-uptick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airbnb Inc. 连续第二个季度提供乏善可陈的业绩指引，表明在夏季旺季到来之前，旅行支出的增长将进一步放缓。该股在盘中交易中下跌约 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/airbnb-sees-growth-slowing-before-summer-travel-uptick</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Duolingo 提升收入前景，每日用户数突破 3000 万</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/duolingo-boosts-revenue-outlook-as-daily-users-top-30-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Duolingo Inc. 上调了全年业绩预期，并公布第一季度收益超出预期，其每月继续吸引约一百万新用户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/duolingo-boosts-revenue-outlook-as-daily-users-top-30-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
